#### Curl Example

```bash
#!/usr/bin/env bash

curl --location --request POST 'http://localhost:8081/logos' \
--header 'Accept: application/json' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{"image": ""}'
```

#### Run Included script [link](blob/master/scripts/curl-jpg.sh)

```bash
LOGO_DETECTION_HOST=http://localhost:8081 scripts/curl-jpg.sh scripts/inference.jpg 
```

`LOGO_DETECTION_HOST`: (env var) Path to host (no trailing slash no /logos)

`scripts/curl-jpg.sh`: (execute) Path to script
